  <entry>
    <title>SL7下安装odoo12</title>
    <link href="http://tanzhixin.github.io/2019/01/29/SL7%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85odoo12/"/>
    <id>http://tanzhixin.github.io/2019/01/29/SL7下安装odoo12/</id>
    <published>2019-01-29T03:16:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-29T16:05:23.032Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>参考 <a href="https://linuxize.com/post/install-odoo-12-on-centos-7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://linuxize.com/post/install-odoo-12-on-centos-7/</a></p><p>缘起：用户管理需求，测试小型CRM及ERP工具，ZOHO相对来说不自由，于是用云服务器作了一个自己可控的系统</p><p>odoo前身是openerp，是挪威一个哥们写的开源ERP系统，对标的是SAP，目前最新版本是odoo12，发展方向是多功能线上管理系统，目标用户是中小型企业，其他就不多说了。</p><p>1 安装Python 3.6</p><p>SL7的一个麻烦就是python36要先找centos7的SCL源的rpm包，把这个安装上去，后面才能和centos7一样，repo里自带的python36包不全，所以要用SCL源里的rh-python36。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>install python36</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#yum install rh-python36 git gcc wget nodejs-less libxslt-devel bzip2-devel openldap-devel libjpeg-devel freetype-devel postgresql-devel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2 创建系统用户odoo2、用户组以及目录：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>创建用户</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#useradd -m -U -r -d /opt/odoo12 -s /bin/bash odoo12</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>3 安装pgsql-10<br>当然要用最新的pg，只能用从官方的源来安装了。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>添加pgsql官方源，安装和配置pgsql10</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#yum install https://download.postgresql.org/pub/repos/yum/10/redhat/rhel-7-x86_64/pgdg-centos10-10-2.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class="line">#yum install postgresql10-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>配置</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#/usr/pgsql-10/bin/postgresql-10-setup initdb -E UTF-8</span><br><span class="line">#systemctl enable postgresql-10</span><br><span class="line">#systemctl start postgresql-10</span><br><span class="line">#su - postgres -c &quot;createuser -s odoo12&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>并且创建一个与系统用户同名的数据库用户，方便认证。</p><p>4 安装pdf工具包</p><p>wkhtmltox软件包是一个开源的命令行工具，它可以将html转换成pdf等其他各种格式<br><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>下载和安装辅助工具软件</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#wget https://github.com/wkhtmltopdf/wkhtmltopdf/releases/download/0.12.1/wkhtmltox-0.12.1_linux-centos7-amd64.rpm</span><br><span class="line">#yum localinstall wkhtmltox-0.12.1_linux-centos7-amd64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>5 下载安装和配置</p><p>首先切换到同名系统用户</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>切换用户</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">su - odoo12</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>从官方git源克隆最新odoo12代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>克隆源</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://www.github.com/odoo/odoo --depth 1 --branch 12.0 /opt/odoo12/odoo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用rh-python36</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scl enable rh-python36 bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建用于odoo的新虚拟环境，并激活；</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /opt/odoo12</span><br><span class="line">python3 -m venv venv</span><br><span class="line">source venv/bin/activate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更新pip，并安装odoo12所需模块，确保顺利满足所有依赖要求，退出虚拟环境</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install -r odoo/requirements.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">deactivate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以odoo12用户名建立本地附加模块目录，退出到超级用户</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir /opt/odoo12/odoo-custom-addons</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建系统配置文件，内容如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#nano /etc/odoo12.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/etc/odoo12.conf</span><br><span class="line">[options]</span><br><span class="line">; This is the password that allows database operations:</span><br><span class="line">admin_passwd = superadmin_passwd</span><br><span class="line">db_host = False</span><br><span class="line">db_port = False</span><br><span class="line">db_user = odoo12</span><br><span class="line">db_password = False</span><br><span class="line">addons_path = /opt/odoo12/odoo/addons, /opt/odoo12/odoo-custom-addons</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>记得修改超级管理密码。</p><p>创建systemd 单元文件来负责服务的启动和停止</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#nano /etc/systemd/system/odoo12.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>/etc/systemd/system/odoo12.service 内容如下</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Unit]</span><br><span class="line">Description=Odoo12</span><br><span class="line">Requires=postgresql-10.service</span><br><span class="line">After=network.target postgresql-10.service</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Service]</span><br><span class="line">Type=simple</span><br><span class="line">SyslogIdentifier=odoo12</span><br><span class="line">PermissionsStartOnly=true</span><br><span class="line">User=odoo12</span><br><span class="line">Group=odoo12</span><br><span class="line">ExecStart=/usr/bin/scl enable rh-python36 -- /opt/odoo12/venv/bin/python3 /opt/odoo12/odoo/odoo-bin -c /etc/odoo12.conf</span><br><span class="line">StandardOutput=journal+console</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Install]</span><br><span class="line">WantedBy=multi-user.target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>存盘后退出。</p><p>更新systemd单元文件并启动odoo服务</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>启动服务</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable odoo12</span><br><span class="line">systemctl start odoo12</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检查服务状态，确保正常运行。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#systemctl status odoo12</span><br><span class="line">#journalctl -u odoo12</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开页面检查安装结果，如果看不到页面，检查端口8069是否开放，把防火墙的firewalld关闭或者打开端口</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://&lt;your_domain_or_IP_address&gt;:8069</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#netstat -lpn</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#firewall-cmd --permanent --zone=public --add-port=8069/tcp</span><br><span class="line">#firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到如下页面即告成功。</p><img src="/2019/01/29/SL7下安装odoo12/odoo-12-centos.png" title="首页">]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;参考 &lt;a href=&quot;https://linuxize.com/post/install-odoo-12-on-centos-7/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;https://linuxize.com/post/install-odoo
      
    
    </summary>
    
    
  </entry>
  
